## 🛠 Local Development (Optional)

If you want to test locally first:

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

Then open http://localhost:3000

## 📦 Why Next.js?

- ✅ Compiles all code ahead of time (no Babel issues)
- ✅ Proper React setup, industry standard
- ✅ Deployed on Vercel in 2 minutes
- ✅ Scales from hobby to 100k users
- ✅ Your code is maintainable long-term

This is production-ready. 🤍
